{"tid":2266019,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"官方: 紅魔險簽辛康納利與世長辭","createTime":"2020-11-01T03:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T14:14:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2a33a2f1521f8d5a1d5df598823da5c4c8d061","tid":2266019,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:02:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108078162716685/posts/1446824112175410/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108078162716685%2Fposts%2F1446824112175410%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh6Eelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=5ddf860d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108078162716685/posts/1446824112175410/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【紅魔<span class=\"red\">險簽</span>辛康納利與世長辭】<br />\n<br />\n飾演第一代占士邦的著名演員辛康納利（Sir Sean Connery) 於 10 月 31 日與世長辭，享年 90 歲。<span class=\"red\">不說不知，他幾乎成為名帥畢士比爵士麾下的曼聯球員。</span><br />\n<br />\n辛康納利除了演戲出色外，亦有不俗球技，曾為著名的愛丁堡球隊 Bonnyrigg Rose 踢過青年軍，亦曾在蘇格蘭聯賽球會 East Fife 試腳。在出演 South Pacific 音樂劇期間，他與一眾演員在曼徹斯特與一支地方球隊對賽，時任曼聯領隊畢士比亦在場，之後更向他開出一份週薪 25 鎊的合約，幾乎是他當時的兩倍人工﹗<br />\n<br />\n不過由於他當時已經 23 歲，考慮到當年職業球員生涯可能到 30 歲便要掛靴，所以辛康納利婉拒了邀請，最後更成為了獲得奧斯卡金像獎的國際巨星。<br />\n<br />\nR.I.P."},{"pid":"87d8f8be1c29f2a4a00f672ecfbdf3a5257ab3e0","tid":2266019,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d49e007b24c9409c1014af02c362e12789ea9f","tid":2266019,"uid":338496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:24:10.000Z","msg":"Wiki咁講，應該係堅嘅<br />\n<br />\nConnery was a keen footballer, having played for Bonnyrigg Rose in his younger days.[32] He was offered a trial with East Fife. While on tour with South Pacific, Connery played in a football match against a local team that Matt Busby, manager of Manchester United, happened to be scouting.[33] According to reports, Busby was impressed with his physical prowess and offered Connery a contract worth &pound;25 a week (equivalent to &pound;703 in 2019) immediately after the game. Connery admits that he was tempted to accept, but he recalls, &quot;I realised that a top-class footballer could be over the hill by the age of 30, and I was already 23. I decided to become an actor and it turned out to be one of my more intelligent moves.&quot;[34]"},{"pid":"f4dcbf1588685be44cbaaad6e2ffdec4016a1506","tid":2266019,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefc925c801b6a6ca853100da21baab41dd997a8","tid":2266019,"uid":201822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"195幾年嘅25磅即係依家幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddc86660773f98d5c374874338280a11fd3f96c","tid":2266019,"uid":201822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eefc925c801b6a6ca853100da21baab41dd997a8","tid":2266019,"uid":201822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"195幾年嘅25磅即係依家幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"屌自膠，睇到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc9d8ce9f36382155c0022dbabe3e877c4de61c","tid":2266019,"uid":261873,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"入紅魔就已經空難死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed2df371c93655a9d40d9edfa50a0ae60677c70","tid":2266019,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T06:41:55.000Z","msg":"係咪傳曼聯第一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/